Speedbreaker/Wildrider/Beastbox

At the Dark Avian, Wildrider tranforms, and helps Dead-End to his feet.
"Better watch yourself next time Dead-End, Mphhh ah  ha ha ha h"
Speedbreaker then walks down and by the cells, and hears Symphony's
computer mutter something about energon low. He opens the cell, not fearing
the scratched up body, and just in case, shoots him dead centre with his
Break Down gun. He then picks up the lifeless body, and puts him in a CR
chamber. If he did try to escape, he would be rudely suprised by the
inefectivness of his body function. He sat and watched the CR chamber.
